{"tid":855221,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"M記早餐全餐食法","createTime":"2018-10-10T02:33:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-24T05:35:24.000Z","uid":13395,"like":16,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c0fd4d7e4b66f250c779c00053eef0a52dc95ba9","tid":855221,"uid":13395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T02:33:17.000Z","msg":"如果以為包提子醬係就咁比你擦乾包食然後就話提子醬係敗筆,你絕對係懵鳩中既懵鳩!<br />\n<br />\n英式鬆餅拿上手都已經知道鞋過中女隻鮑魚,但佢唔同kfc鬆餅,唔會食落有少少融化感漿住個口而帶黎焗香左既甜味,只係得浸乾過西環海味鋪禾麻鮑既刺口感覺,用下腦就知有咩可能jit d提子醬落去就好食?<br />\n<br />\n正如呀叔多次提示,正統既阿美利堅式早晨全餐食法係,先擺包,上搽草莓醬,放扒,再放炒強,灑黑椒,最後蓋包!包鹽係拎黎丟,唔好落!按呢種食法,然後每食兩啖包就咬一啖炸薯餅,以上咬法組合每進行兩次就飲啖朱古力,咁先正統!無錯,去勿當係要叫朱古力,因佢d咖啡難柒飲過屎水!奶茶一樣廢閪!唯一可飲係朱古力、橙汁同鮮奶,鮮奶要飲自己落惠康買,去勿當奴飲乜柒!橙汁太細,加大太貴,過份呃錢,操!故論性價比,應飲熱朱古力!希望你好好記住,唔好每次犯同樣錯誤後要呀叔再提醒你!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/e/ec/C562502d-1-.gif/revision/latest?cb=20111113040815\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fe%2Fec%2FC562502d-1-.gif%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20111113040815&h=d560c9fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"866f63ea91e66c2cd5c98f3b215e51a23109a599","tid":855221,"uid":172844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T02:35:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7a958c2fb6495db93c3cc77175d7d4389610d9c","tid":855221,"uid":10397,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T02:50:16.000Z","msg":"咁點解你唔叫個豬柳強餐?<br />\n平啲仲多塊芝士"},{"pid":"0a6b31ca0b4acecb000b2a93f3427240d0607074","tid":855221,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T02:54:49.000Z","msg":"冇 睇喎 咁長 篇文<br />\n<br />\n不過其實打野用李星都幾好用<br />\n<br />\n前期夠大壓力 <br />\n<br />\n後期開戰好嘅話都贏緊"},{"pid":"7b1c0413e3d9895d61da419b86300874851c6416","tid":855221,"uid":60287,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T02:55:54.000Z","msg":"丟撚左包果醬<br />\n一邊鬆餅配少少糖漿同薯餅<br />\n另一邊配炒強加黑椒<br />\n最後先食熱香餅同豬柳"},{"pid":"5ef8ab0ba45c807da48ce33e19be1578108b7d8b","tid":855221,"uid":125728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T03:03:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8c26c4d0bd90109ec6458dd3014decd6fd14dd1b","tid":855221,"uid":195169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T03:24:07.000Z","msg":"做乜又POST相同嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2e70b8e0037653126db6f0e25538c88973490cf","tid":855221,"uid":96708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:55:09.000Z","msg":"唔洗睇下呢期豬柳期貨個價先決定食唔食？"},{"pid":"81c01be956e1e6c2e66d731e2dc641431f7dfd8d","tid":855221,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T03:03:16.000Z","msg":"老一輩？"},{"pid":"72b9b19cd7c3ddc50dc5cf9469fea019a85024aa","tid":855221,"uid":19218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T03:11:25.000Z","msg":"拎個包浸杯朱古力食，其他野倒左佢"},{"pid":"757e760a0ffcb67414e918e1029498c8fe75ea60","tid":855221,"uid":120481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T05:35:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}